      <content:encoded>&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/YWV4HTHIMJFKZFPBBCJUKRKEEE.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;김영근 기자
